sub_title: Building Software Teams // Any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magicü™Ñ
summary:
‚ÄúAny sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic.‚Äù ‚Äì Sir Arthur C. Clarke

--------
Digital and technology are my natural environments: I am focused on all-things-digital, including engineering, data, technology, online marketing, e-commerce, BI, analytics, and (tech) customer care roles of all levels. 

I have extensive international sourcing and headhunting experience. I have been recruiting for companies based in the Netherlands and hiring local talent for offices outside of the Netherlands.

Recruitment, sourcing, employer branding, candidate experience optimization workshops, coaching, and consultancy are available on demand. Extensive experience in international recruitment setup (including Visa, relocation process etc.), process management, and recruitment KPI reporting.

I speak fluently English, French, Polish, and Dutch. ...and Boolean ;-)
